summary.description:
Today, a bit warmer for the outside temperature (up 3.8°C), feels like temperature (up 3.8°C), and inside temperature (up 3.2°C) and drier conditions in outside humidity (down 10%) and rainfall (down 0.4 mm).

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in rainfall (up 0.4 mm).

The past week and month had observable variation in rainfall (up 0.1 mm), cloud levels (up 475 m), and feels like temperature (up 2.5°C) when compared to today.
